      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a benchmark for its model. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior finish is breathtaking, featuring a deep, mirror-like gloss protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings here. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine leather and flawless trim, retaining its original factory scent with absolutely no signs of bolster wear or aging. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the heated seats, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is in showroom condition, backed by a comprehensive binder of dealership service records documenting preventative maintenance performed well ahead of schedule. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a like-new driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 48500.0,
